A South-African Chorus Book.

these are the source files for this book.

they must be processed with ConTeXt to produce a pdf.

'sorter.py' will try to produce a list of source files in an order that
maximizes the page filling.

the space required for each chorus must be entered in the table inside 
the sorter.py.

